SORA 2 (OPENAI)
OpenAI's video generation model with synchronized audio. 
BF: High-fidelity video with dialogue and sound API: OpenAI API Pricing: Free tier available; Pro from $0.10-0.50/sec depending on resolution 
Capabilities: 
Up to 60 seconds with synchronized audio Dialogue, sound effects, and ambient audio sora-2 (fast) and sora-2-pro (quality) variants Text-to-video and image-to-video 
Ad creative use cases: 
Video testimonials and talking-head style ads Product demo videos with narration Narrative brand videos 
Docs: OpenAI Video Generation 
