PLATFORM-SPECIFIC IMAGE SPECS
When generating images for ads, request the correct dimensions: 
Platform Placement Aspect Ratio Recommended Size Meta Feed Single image 1:1 1080x1080 Meta Stories/Reels Vertical 9:16 1080x1920 Meta Carousel Square 1:1 1080x1080 Google Display Landscape 1.91:1 1200x628 Google Display Square 1:1 1200x1200 LinkedIn Feed Landscape 1.91:1 1200x627 LinkedIn Feed Square 1:1 1200x1200 TikTok Feed Vertical 9:16 1080x1920 Twitter/X Feed Landscape 16:9 1200x675 Twitter/X Card Landscape 1.91:1 800x418 
Include these dimensions in your generation prompts to avoid needing to crop or resize. 